Package: topicsplorrr
Title: A Package Supporting Topical Text Analysis, Exploration and Visualization 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stefan", "Daume", email = "stefan.daume@scitingly.net", 
            role = c("cre", "aut")))
Description: The package provides functions to analyse and visualize the results
    of an STM topic model, including a Shiny application for topic model 
    exploration.
